name: Earth 2: MARS
description:
MARS on Earth 2 was founded in 2032 and quickly grew its community. Establishing itself as an energy transit hub for spacecraft all around the Milky Way. 

Now in 2148, Earth 2's MARS has grown into the main hub for energy and space transportation, with the Milky Way Civil War just ending. Everyone is on high alert and ready to find their own version of a solution, no matter the cost.
